snippet.title: Super Space Slayer 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Space Slayer 2 is ready! Return to the Galaxy with new weapons, new enemies, and an epic new quest to defeat Luciferus once and for all!

Download the game on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.plasmabeamgames.superspaceslayer2

Outtakes: https://youtu.be/hkqzCOhCHuo
